description: A fully object-oriented .Net wrapper for the TrelloAPI.
releaseNotes:
A lot has changed with this release.  Your code WILL break.  Please be sure to read the wiki pages at https://bitbucket.org/gregsdennis/manatee.trello/wiki/Home.

See Trello board for this project at https://trello.com/#board/manatee-trello-net/5144051cbd0da6681200201e.  Feedback and questions are welcome through the board, on StackOverflow, or by emailing littlecrabsolutions@yahoo.com.

Extracted JSON and REST providers into separate assemblies and published them individually on Nuget.
New request queuing engine provides better support for "Store and Forward" feature.
Monitors network connectivity automatically.
Updated logging to be more concise.
Moved request processing to a background thread. No longer prevents application from closing smoothly.
Actions and Notifications now possess all properties.  There are no more subclasses.
Moved to a better underlying architecture, keeping in mind the SOLID principles.
title: Manatee.Trello
